Map created by Hobbitten

Following map contains

-----------------------------------------------------------

- 1 long stage (25/30 minutes gameplay)

- 11 Bosses

- 5 Human items

- 3 Zombie items

- 8 objective items to progress in the map

- 4 kinds of NPCs

- Parkour and lasers

Additonal map info

-----------------------------------------------------------

- The map was created in two weeks and was later optimized

- Created for UNLOZE Mapping Contest in 2022

- The map got third in the contest
